description:
Yes! The 2500 subscriber special is finally here! Oddly, my subscriber count seems to increase by 100 every episode I release. What do we do to celebrate? You will just have to watch to find out.

Thanks to all my subscribers, viewers, and especially... my fans. Thanks for leaving comments, liking my videos, and sharing them with others. For the very few of you who dislike my videos... go hug a creeper!

P.S. I think Etho is starting to lose his mind.
